description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Blakelands Hospital&lt;/strong&gt; has exciting opportunities for theatre practitioners, in order to cope with our increasing demand. We need additional Nurses to join our highly experienced and committed teams. With 2 dedicated Theatres and a 3 Bay Recovery area we are keen to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen within our Theatre Department for an enthusiastic, flexible and motivated theatre practitioner to join our friendly dynamic hard-working theatre team. The work is interesting and varied, the pace is fast but we can offer you a friendly and supportive environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have a passion for delivering the best possible care to our Self Pay, Insured and NHS patients then we would like to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be supported by a proactive and forward-thinking Leadership team and experienced speciality Leads.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our specialities include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Anaesthetics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recovery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Orthopaedics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ophthalmology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Urology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;General Surgery (including laparoscopic)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ear, Nose and Throat (ENT)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Endoscopy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Podiatry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In return we offer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive salary Plus Enhancements (if eligible)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;33 days annual leave inc bank holidays which increase with service (pro rata)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private Healthcare&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contributory Pension Scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Life Assurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent Training and Development Opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free on Site Parking*&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Blakelands Hospital is part of the Ramsay Health Care group and provides clinical care to private, insured and NHS patients.  Ramsay Health Care UK is one of the leading providers of NHS and private patient services in England, with a network of over 30 acute hospitals and Treatment Centres.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All offers of employment will be subject to receipt of a satisfactory Enhanced Disclosure Certificate from the Disclosure and Barring Service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Blakelands Hospital is committed to quality, equality and opportunity for all.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
